      <bioghist>
         <head>Biographical/Historical Information</head>
         <p>N. C. Wyeth was a painter and illustrator; chiefly known
         for his illustrations of children's books and historical
         romances.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>The collection contains 44 illustrations by Wyeth for James
         Boyd's 
         <title render="italic">Drums</title>. Pen and ink sketches on
         cardboard, ranging in size from 3 x 5 inches to 5 x 8 inches.
         Each sketch has a title in the lower left corner and a
         notation in which chapter it will be placed.</p>
      </scopecontent>
